# Frontend Standards

## Component Structure
- Use **functional components only** with TypeScript — no class components
- One component per file; filename matches the component name (PascalCase)
- Co-locate styles with the component using Tailwind classes — no separate CSS files
- Use `shadcn/ui` components as the base; extend with Tailwind, don't override

## TypeScript
- All props must have a typed interface defined above the component
- Use `interface` for props, `type` for unions/intersections
- No `any` types — use `unknown` + type narrowing if needed

```tsx
// ✅ GOOD
interface EcoScoreRingProps {
  score: number;        // 0–10
  size?: "sm" | "md" | "lg";
  showLabel?: boolean;
}

export function EcoScoreRing({ score, size = "md", showLabel = true }: EcoScoreRingProps) { ... }

// ❌ BAD
export function EcoScoreRing(props: any) { ... }
```

## Data Fetching
- Use `fetch` with `async/await` in Server Components where possible (Next.js App Router)
- For client-side fetching, use SWR or React Query — no raw `useEffect` + `fetch` combos
- All API calls go through `/lib/api.ts` — never fetch directly from a component

## State Management
- Use Zustand for global state (selected persona, user preferences, cart/booking state)
- Keep component state local with `useState` when it doesn't need to be shared
- The active persona store lives in `/store/persona.ts`

## Mobile-First
- Design for 390px (iPhone 15) base width first
- All interactive elements must be at least 44×44px touch target
- Use Tailwind's `sm:` / `md:` breakpoints to enhance for larger screens

## Mapbox
- Map component lives in `/components/map/LocalPartnerMap.tsx`
- Always lazy-load with `dynamic(() => import(...), { ssr: false })` — Mapbox breaks with SSR
- Store Mapbox token in `NEXT_PUBLIC_MAPBOX_TOKEN` env var

## File Structure
```
frontend/
├── app/                   # Next.js App Router pages
├── components/            # Reusable UI components
│   ├── eco/               # EcoScoreRing, EcoSubScoreBreakdown, etc.
│   ├── brief/             # ArrivalBriefCard, BriefSection, etc.
│   ├── map/               # LocalPartnerMap, PartnerCard, etc.
│   ├── profile/           # PreferencesSection, BadgeShelf, etc.
│   └── ui/                # shadcn/ui re-exports
├── lib/                   # API client, utils, constants
├── store/                 # Zustand stores
├── types/                 # Shared TypeScript types
└── public/                # Static assets
```
